list.abstract: signature（英[ˈsɪɡnətʃə]，美[ˈsɪɡnətʃər]），英语单词，名词，译为署名；签名；折标；标记。短语搭配有key signature（调号）。例句为“Acceleration is the signature of our time.（加速是我们这个时代的标志。）” 该单词的近义词为a scratch of pen，复数形式为signatures。
Signature是一个舞蹈团体，成员为Sulaman和Maddu，他们是英国达人第二季亚军，他们的演出非常有创意，以Michael Jackson的模仿秀为主，添加了很多印度的元素，印度舞里混搭太空步。

yingyinNormal.en: Documents don't go away. Your signature doesn't go away.
yingyinNormal.zh: 文件不会消失，你的签名不会消失。

yingyinNormal.en: You forged my signature? Did Mrs. Applebaum pay you a visit?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你伪造了我的签名? Applebaum夫人去见过你了吗?

yingyinNormal.en: Actually, I have your signature on a roommate agreement. That says you do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 事实上，从你在室友协议上签名的那天起，你就注定得忍受。

yingyinNormal.en: Why? It says "keep this on your person at all times." It's right here under batman's signature.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为什么？它上面写着"请随时随身携持本证"，就在蝙蝠侠签名的下面。

yingyinNormal.en: Some of them advertise. Do they really? Serial killing is an expression of power, ego, a signature in human destruction.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有些连环杀手爱宣扬。真的吗？连环杀人是种力量 ，自负的炫耀，是毁灭生命的签名。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you crazy? That helmet's signed by Robert Downey Jr. So? Okay, if you're going to question the importance of an actor's signature on a plastic helmet from a movie based on a comic book, then all of our lives have no meaning!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你疯了吗？那头盔上有小罗伯特·唐尼的签名。那又怎样？好吧，如果你要质疑一个来自漫画改编的电影，还有演员签名的塑料头盔的重要性，那我们这群人的生活还有什么意义可言！

yingyinNormal.en: Yup, that's our signature. Got us bounced out of Six Flags.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没错，这是我们的招牌，害我们去主题公园时被赶出来。

yingyinNormal.en: There must be some parliamentary procedure that will nullify my signature.
yingyinNormal.zh: 肯定有什么议事规则可以撤销我的签字。

yingyinNormal.en: He wants you to find it. It's been taken. It emits a gamma signature that's too weak for us to trace.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他希望你能找到它，魔方被抢了，目前它散发的伽马射线太微弱，我们追踪不到。

yingyinNormal.en: I remember your signature on those papers, Colonel. That's right. And I'm pretty sure I paid for that. You have second thoughts? Not anymore.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我记得你也签了那份文件，中校。是啊。我也为此付出了代价。你后悔了吗？现在没了。

yingyinNormal.en: I think if it were exposed to a sufficiently powerful energy source something very similar to its own signature, perhaps its molecular integrity could fail.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我觉得如果它遭遇足够强大的能量源特性类似其本身的能量，那或许它的分子完整性就会被破坏。
